original: Bjartmar, Carl Gunnar Harald, tandläkare, Linköping, f. 31/3/07 i Hudiksvall. G. 34 m. tandl. Inez Boi-vie. Barn: Ulf Harald f. 35, Christina 37, Agneta 41, Ulla 45. — Stud:ex. v. Sthlm-s samgymn. 27, Cand. med. dent. i Freiburg im Breisgau 30, tysk tandl. där 32, sv. dito 34. Assist, o. vik. i Nynäshamn, Karlstad o. Södertälje 34-35, i Sthlm 35-37, prakt, i Linköping sed. 37.
translated: Bjartmar, Carl Gunnar Harald, dentist, Linköping, born March 31, 1907 in Hudiksvall. Married in 1934 to dentist Inez Boi-vie. Children: Ulf Harald born 1935, Christina born 1937, Agneta born 1941, Ulla born 1945. Education: graduated from Sthlm-s samgymn in 1927, received a degree in dental medicine from Freiburg im Breisgau in 1930, worked as a German dentist there in 1932 and as a Swedish dentist in 1934. Worked as an assistant and substitute dentist in Nynäshamn, Karlstad, and Södertälje from 1934-1935, and in Stockholm from 1935-1937. Practiced dentistry in Linköping from 1937 onwards.
